        Bankmybiz.com is a matching network of business owners and lenders. As an entrepreneur, time is your most precious commodity. We'll <strong>save you time</strong> and <strong>help get you the financing you need</strong> by informing you about which funding products you qualify for and then connect you directly with local and national lenders. 
