    <section id="relationshipsLenders">
      <h1 class='text-center'><i class="icon ion-beaker"></i> Relationship Lending</h1>
      <p>
        We believe in Relationship Lending. Having a relationship with a lender means a lot for the health and future success of your business. When you are looking for funding, you might really just be thinking about this next deal, but it is important to treat this deal as an opportunity to lay the relationships groundwork for the next and the next and the next.
      </p>
      <p>
        A lender is more than just a source of funding. Lenders are super connectors and mavens inside of business networks. When you work together they have all the incentive to make introductions for you to potential customers, suppliers, and ancillary services such as accountants and lawyers. 
      </p>
      <p>
        The internet is a fast and easy way to make connections, build trust, and start and continue relationships. On  Bankmybiz.com we provide a way to make connections fast and build trust and relationships from the comfort of your desktop or mobile phone. 
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="challenges">
      <h1 class='text-center'><i class="icon ion-ios7-chatboxes-outline"></i> Challenges & Advice</h1>
      <p>
        The home page of Bankmybiz.com is a <strong>stream of challenges and questions</strong> about business, financing, banking, and any other interesting or helpful thing that the network creates. Post challenges and advice about your industry and business to get advice (or feedback) and receive <strong>Bankmybiz Cred</strong>. The Bankmybiz.com network is where you can get advice and demonstrate your thought-leadership in your industry.
      </p>
      <p>
        You control the solicitation of lenders on Bankmybiz.com. Businesses can contact lenders and other business owners, but you must put lenders in your pipeline or be a match for them to reach out to you. By asking questions and posting advice, you are building connections and demonstrating your expertise. Try it out today.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you see a challenge you share or some advice that you think is right on the money, <strong> vote it up!</strong>. By voting questions, answers, and comments up the poster receives </strong>Bankmybiz Cred</strong> which shows their credibility and value to the Bankmybiz.com Network. On the other hand, if you see something wrong or not helpful, <strong>vote it down</strong>. This communicates that that user could be more helpful than their being.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="matches">
      <h1 class='text-center'><i class="icon ion-shuffle"></i> Product & <br> <i class="icon ion-ios7-people-outline"></i> Lender Matches</h1>
