        Bankmybiz is a <strong>Small Business Funding Matching Platform</strong>, this means we match you funding products and strategies you qualify for and we match you with lenders that specialize in funding businesses like yours.
      </p>
      <p>
        It <strong>takes 5 minutes</strong> to complete your profile. We don't require overburdensome financials to get started with your profile. We match you on just a few fields including your industry, revenue size, employee size, business type, number of years a business has filed taxes, and location.
      </p>
      <p>
        Bankmybiz.com matches you with the funding products that you most likely qualify for. You can use Bankmybiz.com no matter what stage of business you are in. Just answer each question on your profile and you will immediately get suggestions for products and lenders.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="milestones">
