        Use your Bankmybiz.com <strong>Pipeline</strong> to stay up to date with the activity of the lenders and business owners you want to learn from or do business with. By adding users to your Pipeline you will receive updates when they post challenges and advice or reach milestones. Treat your Bankmybiz.com Pipeline like a CRM of your funding prospects.
      </p>
      <p>
